# <type>[optional scope]: <concise description> [(#issue)]
#
# Use a single-line commit message only. Do not add a detailed body.
# Common types: feat, fix, refactor, chore, tests, docs, build.
# Use tests for all test-code-only changes, including fixes, refactoring, and test infrastructure updates.
#
# Examples:
#   fix: Correct tax amount rounding (#123)
#   tests: Stabilize invoice loading scenario
